{
  "stem": "14156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the translation is like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], what means as our comrades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That means when the Jewish blood from the, from the knife runs down the knife, then things will go twice as good for us in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hang the Juden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hang the Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] was the communist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father and I were standing on the second floor and just put the, the, the drapes a little on the side, trying to see as they marched by.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those were children, kids I went to school together with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it, it, it just felt to me that it's, it's time to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- you know, you cannot-- we cannot stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That, you know, that that was one of the first imprints on my life that I'd seen what they are going to do to us, that how we, we, we, we, we are just nobody.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are nothing-- dirt, like you would call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that-- OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's, that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father just in the beginning, he just waved it off a little.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And but it, it came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It, you know, it kept on going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It got bigger and bigger and bigger in, in all kinds of ways like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father besides we had a store-- we sold clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means suits for men mostly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or we also had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the, the, the material to make the clothes, to make, you know, where you needed a, a, a, a tailor to do this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people used to come to the store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father fitted them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
